<p>---</p>
<h2>🔒 Security</h2>
<strong>SearXNG SSRF Protection:</strong> The SearXNG instance URL is validated with defense-in-depth:
<li>Enforces `http`/`https` schemes only</li>
<li>Blocks cloud metadata endpoints (169.254.169.254, metadata.google.internal)</li>
<li>Resolves hostnames and blocks private/internal IPs (loopback, RFC1918, link-local, reserved)</li>
<li>Operators who intentionally self-host on private networks can set `SEARXNG_ALLOW_PRIVATE=1`</li>
